---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="description" content="Cat Gogh Studio blends software development and digital art into immersive brand experiences." />
    <title>Cat Gogh Studio | Software + Digital Art</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p>Welcome to Cat Gogh Studio</p>
        <h1>Where engineering precision meets digital artistry.</h1>
        <p>
          Cat Gogh Studio started as a sketchbook full of feline characters and grew into a creative technology studio
          helping brands ship software products wrapped in unforgettable visual storytelling.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story-grid" aria-label="Studio pillars">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Chapter 1: Curiosity</h2>
          <p>
            We began with a simple question: why should apps feel sterile? Cat Gogh Studio explored how playful art,
            character design, and narrative can make interfaces more human and memorable.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Chapter 2: Craft</h2>
          <p>
            Today we build modern web experiences, internal tools, and custom digital products with clean architecture,
            maintainable code, and thoughtful interaction design.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Chapter 3: Fusion</h2>
          <p>
            Our unique value is the fusion: software development plus digital art direction. You get robust products and
            a visual identity that feels distinctly yours.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="timeline" aria-label="Studio timeline">
        <h2>The Cat Gogh Story</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>2019:</strong> First illustrated prototypes launched for indie creators.</li>
          <li><strong>2021:</strong> Expanded into full-stack development for startups and creative agencies.</li>
          <li><strong>2023:</strong> Introduced digital mural packs, animated assets, and interactive brand worlds.</li>
          <li><strong>2026:</strong> Continuing to deliver software that performs beautifully and art that works hard.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="cta">
        <h2>Build something vivid.</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you need a production-ready app, a digital art campaign, or both, Cat Gogh Studio can bring your
          story to life.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@catgogh.studio">Start your project</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
